&lt;li&gt;Experience building full three statement models (forward/backward), including all key KPIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct experience reviewing credit agreements and bond indentures in order to understand corporate balance sheet flexibility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior industry specific focus and experience preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
